arts.ttl: Darmstadt exact brutal revenge on Schalke with cup victory
arts.sum: Darmstadt progressed to the Round of 16 in the DFB-Pokal with a 4-0 victory over fellow 2. Bundesliga side Schalke 04.

arts.ttl: SV Darmstadt vs. Schalke 04: DFB-Pokal preview, team news & predicted lineups
arts.sum: Florian Kohfeldt’s SV Darmstadt welcome Miron Muslic’s high-flying Schalke 04 to the Merck-Stadion am Böllenfalltor on Wednesday evening for their second meeting in just five days.
